data.title: Local Neighbourhood BYO Mediterranean Bistro
data.text:
BONDI’S LOCAL NEIGHBOURHOOD

BYo bistro

A little neighbourhood gem located on Curlewis Street in Bondi Beach, Brown Sugar has been an institution in Bondi for 25 years.

Brown Sugar is an intimate 48-seater Mediterranean Bistro frequented by locals, foodie enthusiasts and wine lovers; being one of the few restaurants to still offer BYO (wine).

Bringing a small slice of the Mediterranean to Bondi Beach our produce is sourced fresh daily from local suppliers to bring an offering that is unique and seasonal, with a living wine list to match.

Brown Sugar is run by a small team of passionate industry professionals committed to delivering the most memorable relaxed fine dining experience, ready to ensure each visit is as magical as the next.

We can’t wait to welcome you!

BOOK A TABLE

Menu

Our philosophy is simple: We endeavour to bring a small slice of the Mediterranean to Bondi Beach, through unique and seasonal menu offerings.

Inspired by the flavours of the Mediterranean, our chefs are dedicated to sourcing the finest quality local produce to comprise our delicious seasonal menu. Cooked with care and passion, you’ll find our dishes bursting with full flavours and creative flair.
